title: Ep. #138 | Catching Up: Raisa
description:
Eric calls up Indonesian solo artist Raisa to chat about how music came into her life, her big plans for the future, and her recent collaboration with singer-songwriter Sam Kim!

Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
